ontinue\n```\n\nall good now\n```\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,951::INFO::[newsunpack:1041] Quick-check for Howard The Duck 003 (2015) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire).cbr is OK, skipping repair\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,952::DEBUG::[filesystem:932] [sabnzbd.newsunpack.par2_repair] Deleting file \\\\?\\C:\\sab\\downloads\\incomplete\\Howard_The_Duck_003__2015___Digital___BlackManta-Empire___cbr\\Howard The Duck 003 (2015) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire).cbr.par2\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,952::DEBUG::[filesystem:932] [sabnzbd.newsunpack.par2_repair] Deleting file \\\\?\\C:\\sab\\downloads\\incomplete\\Howard_The_Duck_003__2015___Digital___BlackManta-Empire___cbr\\Howard The Duck 003 (2015) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire).cbr.vol0+1.par2\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,953::DEBUG::[filesystem:932] [sabnzbd.newsunpack.par2_repair] Deleting file \\\\?\\C:\\sab\\downloads\\incomplete\\Howard_The_Duck_003__2015___Digital___BlackManta-Empire___cbr\\Howard The Duck 003 (2015) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire).cbr.vol1+2.par2\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,954::DEBUG::[filesystem:932] [sabnzbd.newsunpack.par2_repair] Deleting file \\\\?\\C:\\sab\\downloads\\incomplete\\Howard_The_Duck_003__2015___Digital___BlackManta-Empire___cbr\\Howard The Duck 003 (2015) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire).cbr.vol3+3.par2\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,954::DEBUG::[filesystem:521] build_filelists(): joinables: []\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,955::DEBUG::[filesystem:522] build_filelists(): rars: []\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,955::DEBUG::[filesystem:523] build_filelists(): 7zips: []\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,955::DEBUG::[filesystem:524] build_filelists(): ts: []\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,956::DEBUG::[postproc:984] Deobfuscate: rarvolnr is: {}\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,956::DEBUG::[postproc:985] Deobfuscate: volnrext is: {}\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,956::DEBUG::[postproc:839] Verified sets: {'Howard The Duck 003 (2015) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire).cbr': True}\n2025-07-16 12:24:05,957::DEBUG::[filesystem:1110] [sabnzbd.postproc.parring] Saving data for __verified__ in \\\\?\\C:\\sab\\downl